            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-7888bb096038db6c-3b1939 twpub-7888bb096038db6c-8bcce8 twpub-7888bb096038db6c-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"pgmonospaced pgheader\">\n<br>The Project Gutenberg EBook of Fo Shuo Wu Liang Shou Jing, by Unknown\n<br>\n<br>This eBook is for the use of anyone anywhere at no cost and with\n<br>almost no restrictions whatsoever.  You may copy it, give it away or\n<br>re-use it under the terms of the Project Gutenberg License included\n<br>with this eBook or online at www.gutenberg.org\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>Title: Fo Shuo Wu Liang Shou Jing\n<br>\n<br>Author: Unknown\n<br>\n<br>Translator: Zeng Kai Kang\n<br>\n<br>Release Date: May 17, 2008 [EBook #25498]\n<br>\n<br>Language: Chinese\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>*** START OF THIS PROJECT GUTENBERG EBOOK FO SHUO WU LIANG SHOU JING ***\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>Produced by Winnie Zhou\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br></div></div>"
